{"tid":85712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英提出思考在郊野公園建屋","createTime":"2017-01-18T13:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T02:44:52.000Z","uid":34286,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"478b2b9be0e99a32873d6036fd0c2db37879ed2b","tid":85712,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英發表任內最後一份施政報告，宣布多項新基建，並總結在土地房屋政策的經驗，提出要思考在郊野公園建屋。 <br />\n<br />\n重中之重的房屋政策推行多年，梁振英承認公屋用地供應仍然落後，公屋輪候時間明顯延長。他在最後一份施政報告呼籲社會思考要用郊野公園內生態價值不高，位於邊陲地帶的土地興建公營房屋或者老人院。"},{"pid":"5d67a67b452b085b34d6d4a25c99691bc263fae7","tid":85712,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR，你支持嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc23c9a10adf96207b6e327f608c5cf71fbef64","tid":85712,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db136b35fb50b1b53a1bd1f087246ab6ef0cb75b","tid":85712,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"On9 源頭問題唔搞，搞郊野公園<br />\n今日150個，十年二十年之後，用盡所有山填哂海都唔夠啦，香港咁細<br />\n仲有，樓價問題又唔搞，d豪宅起出黎係炒唔係住，根本最有需要嘅人嘅買唔到，幾多地都冇用啦"},{"pid":"d262c122f0f33e6965dd10749dabc1531e8b6834","tid":85712,"uid":69957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就要，人都冇得住，仲話保護環境，成件事好荒謬，環保撚先係最離地</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環保撚一係以後露營住深山<br />\n我覺得夠用就好<br />\n但宜家擺明係唔夠地發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 唔好再比蝗蟲繁殖先是重點"},{"pid":"1b10ded6d75610192135a3fda1db0bfae8644989","tid":85712,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 源頭問題唔搞，搞郊野公園<br />\n今日150個，十年二十年之後，用盡所有山填哂海都唔夠啦，香港咁細<br />\n仲有，樓價問題又唔搞，d豪宅起出黎係炒唔係住，根本最有需要嘅人嘅買唔到，幾多地都冇用啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一 人口來源-新移民<br />\n第二 地產商/新界鄉紳囤積既土地<br />\n第三 新界大量棕地<br />\n<br />\n政府冇一樣敢搞<br />\n就搞郊野公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比你剷晒所有郊野公園都唔會夠人住囉"},{"pid":"fd5d4b7bfe5c91e929f9d5c1b2b75e69079b8bea","tid":85712,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"全部建公屋就支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162565d0d580e915fe10f504c2dce322edbca6cf","tid":85712,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63c38832e80138ccd0728e0fdd72799fae309b96","tid":85712,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"好多近市區仆野公園應該起公屋啦，唔打激樓市點打激新來港人仕。垃圾香港無人來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdec570f6eba341b4f16f89dcc57f37e3c1302f","tid":85712,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"支持填平個維港佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f10cae9e1548b2424ac8801088d9f9d712324","tid":85712,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多近市區<span style=\"color: red;\">仆</span>野公園應該起公屋啦，唔打<span style=\"color: red;\">激</span>樓市點打激新來港人仕。垃圾香港無人來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c84dee83ffe30141ea883c1bf3a224c157d55d3","tid":85712,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9b1a275740d24d62b4aa8c19460bf94c2266537","tid":85712,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20